#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.69"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.69:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.69:0.2"
msgid "7. Pattakammavagga "
msgstr "7. Deeds of Substance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.69:0.3"
msgid "69. Padhānasutta "
msgstr "69. Effort "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.74, sc1
msgctxt "an4.69:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, padhānāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four efforts. "

msgctxt "an4.69:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.69:1.3"
msgid "Saṃvarappadhānaṃ, pahānappadhānaṃ, bhāvanāppadhānaṃ, anurakkhaṇāppadhānaṃ. "
msgstr "The efforts to restrain, to give up, to develop, and to preserve. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.69:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, saṃvarappadhānaṃ? "
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to restrain? "

msgctxt "an4.69:1.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. "
msgstr "It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so that bad, unskillful qualities don’t arise. "

msgctxt "an4.69:1.6"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saṃvarappadhānaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the effort to restrain. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.69:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, pahānappadhānaṃ? "
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to give up? "

msgctxt "an4.69:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. "
msgstr "It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so that bad, unskillful qualities are given up. "

msgctxt "an4.69:2.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pahānappadhānaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the effort to give up. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.69:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, bhāvanāppadhānaṃ? "
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to develop? "

msgctxt "an4.69:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. "
msgstr "It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so that skillful qualities arise. "

msgctxt "an4.69:3.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhāvanāppadhānaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the effort to develop. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.69:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, anurakkhaṇāppadhānaṃ? "
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to preserve? "

msgctxt "an4.69:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. "
msgstr "It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so that skillful qualities that have arisen remain, are not lost, but increase, mature, and are fulfilled by development. "

msgctxt "an4.69:4.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, anurakkhaṇāppadhānaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the effort to preserve. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.69:4.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri padhānānīti. "
msgstr "These are the four efforts. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.69:5.1"
msgid "Saṃvaro ca pahānañca, "
msgstr "Restraint and giving up, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.2"
msgid "bhāvanā anurakkhaṇā; "
msgstr "development and preservation: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.3"
msgid "Ete padhānā cattāro, "
msgstr "these are the four efforts "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.4"
msgid "desitādiccabandhunā; "
msgstr "taught by the Kinsman of the Sun. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: hi → yehi (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.69:5.5"
msgid "Yo hi bhikkhu idhātāpī, "
msgstr "Any mendicant who keenly applies these "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.6"
msgid "khayaṃ dukkhassa pāpuṇe”ti. "
msgstr "may attain the ending of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.69:5.7"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
